data.description: Excellent 2 Family house in mint condition and located in the heart of Jamaica. This property features 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, 2 kitchens and a full finished basement with separate entrance. Hardwood floors throughout the building, granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances. Pvt driveway and parking for up to three vehicles. Back and front yard space, and 24 hrs. cc security system. The house is conveniently located near public transportation, shopping, dining and houses of worship. This property is a must see.
